verbose_text: Serum levels of pro inflammatory cytokines interleukin (IL)-1, IL-8, high-sensitivity C-reactive protein (hs-CRP), and tumor necrosis factor (TNF)-alpha as well as beta-endorphin were measured by enzyme linked immunosorbent assay.
